{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"2de4293eb7cb4e04","type":"text","text":"## Personal archival and knowledge management\n> I want to remember and retrieve articles that I've read, or my thoughts about them.\n> \n> I want to prioritize articles that I am yet to read.","x":-1064,"y":34,"width":429,"height":246},
		{"id":"ef3f68260bccf851","type":"text","text":"## Readup as a Public Library\n> Readup is like a library of articles on the internet (like *Goodreads for articles*?). Every item in it was hand-imported by a reader. I want to be able to search this library, go to certain sections, and discover new articles.","x":-1043,"y":-349,"width":447,"height":243,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"72d71d5603df2359","type":"text","text":"### [[Proxy Reader Fork or Feature]]","x":-400,"y":1402,"width":240,"height":50,"color":"#d1e2b0"},
		{"id":"fb906c9e242d7e06","type":"text","text":"## Article Intake & Discovery\n\n> I want Readup to help me find new articles to read, from sources that I'm interested in. ","x":-851,"y":-669,"width":432,"height":176,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"0cf377b6f801b716","type":"text","text":"## Marketing, Communication & Community\n> Readup, as a social network, is more fun if more people are involved. I want more people to know about Readup.","x":-294,"y":-765,"width":434,"height":184,"color":"#ffd8c8"},
		{"id":"75ecf0c462206c43","type":"text","text":"## Readup as a Reading Club\n> I want to meet new people through articles & comments, and stay in touch with their reading.","x":224,"y":-708,"width":391,"height":191,"color":"#d28a82"},
		{"id":"259be0fc0be21404","type":"text","text":"## Availability\n> I want to be able to read using Readup on all my screens, in any situation.","x":-340,"y":574,"width":374,"height":152,"color":"#d1e2b0"},
		{"id":"053dceda25846076","type":"text","text":"## Reading experience\n> I want to be able to read any article comfortably on Readup.","x":-774,"y":375,"width":355,"height":179,"color":"#909e9c"},
		{"id":"780889746ffadf52","type":"text","text":"### [[Monetization|Monetization]]","x":1127,"y":816,"width":206,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"8edcb6b8956345d7","type":"text","text":"### [[Onboarding for writers|Writer-specific onboarding]]","x":700,"y":794,"width":332,"height":102,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"6e91cba1c7bc4b0d","type":"text","text":"### [[Automated verification]]","x":1121,"y":1024,"width":300,"height":94,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"9ffaeec052cc1413","type":"text","text":"### [[Publishing platform plugins|Publishing platform plugins]]","x":727,"y":1071,"width":334,"height":103,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"037a5fffafd3830c","type":"text","text":"## Habit forming, [[Readup Evolution/Auto-tracking in the extension|tracking]] & gamification\n> I want Readup to motivate me to read more (long-form) articles.","x":131,"y":545,"width":357,"height":181,"color":"#d286a5"},
		{"id":"d2de6b90d8ee2471","type":"text","text":"#### [[Webmentions|Webmentions]]","x":1787,"y":-87,"width":213,"height":67,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"bccb13551760f891","type":"text","text":"#### [[Auto-send Readup comments to external writer accounts|On Mastodon]]","x":1787,"y":97,"width":213,"height":63,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"147dc011fbce17a9","type":"text","text":"### On Mastodon, Twitter/X, ...","x":1713,"y":-503,"width":324,"height":73,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"568eca4d8f0508da","type":"text","text":"## External connections\n>  I want my social actions on Readup to have effects outside Readup, so I can reach more people with my thoughts on articles that I've read.\n>","x":570,"y":-426,"width":492,"height":194,"color":"4"},
