		{"id":"2eac42648a257c12","type":"text","text":"## For writers & publications\n> I want to share my writing with readers, and engage with readers","x":576,"y":408,"width":417,"height":166,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"5a82cd0ea6b3e791","type":"text","text":"## Self-hosting & Internationalization\n> As a reader that reads in languages other than English, I want a Readup instance for my language, region or culture.\n> \n> As a general community organizer, I like local communities, and I want Readup software to support my local reading club.","x":604,"y":-78,"width":466,"height":286,"color":"#ffbcfb"},
